<section role="banner" aria-label="repurposing-research" class="page-header header--purple">
  <div class="header-content__container role-page">
    <div class="header-content__left">
      <%= image_tag 'test-user-img.png', class: 'user-role-img' %>
    </div>
    <div class="header-content__right">
      <h6 class="title__inverse uppercase">Funders</h6>
      <h3 class="title__inverse">Why Join CureAccelerator?</h3>
      <p class="title__inverse">You want your dollars to create tangible impact and solutions for the patients you care about most. CureAccelerator provides a network of researchers and support options for individual funders as well as organizations, with a central focus on repurposing for maximum impact. Learn more about repurposing here.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up', ' https://app.cureaccelerator.org/registration', class: 'button button--white button--header' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section role="region" aria-label="clinicians-features" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">What can I do with CureAccelerator?</h6>
  </header>
  <div class="page-section--body">
    <h1 class="title" id="clinicians-features">Do more good more quickly by tapping into a  global community committed to repurposing</h1>
    <p class="text">CureAccelerator’s community is composed of like-minded people who are dedicated to creating effective treatments through repurposing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-layout">
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon difference">Difference</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Make a difference with your dollars</h5>
      <p>Post a Request for Proposal (RFP) with your specific requests, and access a community of researchers and clinicians committed to repurposing. Or browse existing projects to find a match for yourself or your organization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon benefit">Benefit</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Benefit from scientific review</h5>
      <p>Respond to current Requests for Proposals (RFPs), or receive funding pledges on your proposals. Through discussion boards and member connections, you can receive and provide feedback on the Proposals and RFPs of others.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon work">Work</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Work together with others</h5>
      <p>Collaborate with like-minded funders to create greater leverage and support for the patient populations you care about the most.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon global-3">Global</i>
